1:06:24.937 --> 1:06:26.372
The world is full of messages.

1:06:26.406 --> 1:06:29.276
Trim, lean,
abs in just minutes...

1:06:29.308 --> 1:06:30.477
Do
this and you'll be happy.

1:06:30.509 --> 1:06:32.111
Change that and
you'll be a success.

1:06:32.145 --> 1:06:34.047
Lose weight, be perfect.

1:06:34.080 --> 1:06:37.151
Beautiful,
handmade jewelry.

1:06:38.183 --> 1:06:39.785
Accomplish.

1:06:39.819 --> 1:06:41.221
I love you.

1:06:43.056 --> 1:06:44.257
I love you.

1:06:44.290 --> 1:06:46.794
Make a lot of money
and you'll be happy.

1:06:49.129 --> 1:06:50.163
But I'm not.

1:06:50.196 --> 1:06:51.797
Ah!

1:06:51.830 --> 1:06:53.499
Wish I could be happy like that.

1:06:53.533 --> 1:06:54.567
Do you really?

1:06:54.600 --> 1:06:56.303
Of course, who wouldn't?

1:06:56.335 --> 1:06:58.437
