1:07:04.477 --> 1:07:06.513
I wish I could
be happy like that.

1:07:08.781 --> 1:07:10.783
Just think of the scuff marks.

1:07:17.189 --> 1:07:19.125
I gotta tell ya'
somethin', Fixer.

1:07:19.158 --> 1:07:22.261
You're probably the best friend.

1:07:22.294 --> 1:07:25.498
Actually, you're the only
friend that I have ever had.

1:07:25.531 --> 1:07:28.634
But I just don't understand why.

1:07:28.667 --> 1:07:30.202
Why all this?

1:07:30.236 --> 1:07:33.306
Why do you insist on doing
all of this every night?

1:07:33.339 --> 1:07:35.275
Why is it so important?

1:07:37.109 --> 1:07:38.745
I came here thinking
I'd get an answer,

1:07:38.777 --> 1:07:40.212
but I still don't know.

1:07:40.245 --> 1:07:42.749
Talk to God every day.

1:07:43.783 --> 1:07:46.051
For at least an hour.

1:07:46.085 --> 1:07:48.221
Be yourself with Him.

1:07:48.254 --> 1:07:50.089
Tell Him everything.

1:07:51.790 --> 1:07:54.393
But the rest of the time,

1:07:54.426 --> 1:07:56.962
the other 23 hours of the day,

1:07:56.995 --> 1:08:00.633
a person must enlist
all their strength

1:08:00.667 --> 1:08:03.370
to be joyful at all times.

1:08:03.402 --> 1:08:08.107
It's human nature to be drawn
to depression and sadness

1:08:08.140 --> 1:08:09.843
because of life's daily events.

1:08:09.875 --> 1:08:14.513
Believe me, everyone is
filled with suffering.

1:08:14.547 --> 1:08:16.884
No matter how it
looks on the outside.

1:08:17.884 --> 1:08:20.953
That is why you

1:08:20.987 --> 1:08:22.589
must force yourself

1:08:22.621 --> 1:08:25.959
to be joyous at all times.

1:08:27.594 --> 1:08:29.997
To make yourself happy

1:08:31.363 --> 1:08:32.299
in any way possible.

1:08:35.033 --> 1:08:36.769
Even with silliness

1:08:37.670 --> 1:08:38.806
if necessary.

1:08:40.739 --> 1:08:41.575
Ah!

1:08:43.408 --> 1:08:45.478
How does she look?

1:08:45.511 --> 1:08:47.046
Looks good to me.

1:08:53.952 --> 1:08:55.855
My life is unfolding.

1:08:55.889 --> 1:08:57.457
Whether I'm doing
it right or not,

1:08:57.489 --> 1:08:59.059
I don't want to waste it.

1:08:59.091 --> 1:09:00.960
If I could have faith
that You're with me

1:09:00.993 --> 1:09:03.729
in every decision, even
the seemingly wrong ones,

1:09:03.763 --> 1:09:07.768
then maybe my life would
be a life of meaning.

1:09:08.968 --> 1:09:10.336
She said,

1:09:14.706 --> 1:09:17.576
ask for what you want

1:09:17.609 --> 1:09:18.911
like

1:09:20.145 --> 1:09:21.982
you already have it.

1:09:23.148 --> 1:09:25.117
Thank you, God,

1:09:27.319 --> 1:09:28.589
for healing me.

1:09:36.028 --> 1:09:38.598
Thank you for
sending me my soulmate.

1:09:39.765 --> 1:09:43.603
Thank you for getting
me off all those meds.

1:09:45.071 --> 1:09:47.806
Maybe I'm here to find you,
in,

1:09:47.840 --> 1:09:49.176
in myself,

1:09:50.242 --> 1:09:52.545
in others,

1:09:55.148 --> 1:09:56.984
in everything around me

1:09:58.952 --> 1:10:02.088
then every moment

1:10:02.121 --> 1:10:05.025
would be my life's purpose.

1:10:05.058 --> 1:10:07.861
Every moment would be my song.

1:10:07.894 --> 1:10:09.830
Who are you?

1:10:15.367 --> 1:10:18.437
Every breath, every thought,

1:10:18.470 --> 1:10:21.073
every word,

1:10:21.107 --> 1:10:22.743
every movement,

1:10:24.943 --> 1:10:26.647
is that why I'm here?

1:10:27.947 --> 1:10:30.450
To find you in it?

1:10:31.584 --> 1:10:33.620
Why are we dancing?

1:10:33.653 --> 1:10:36.356
Maybe because
it makes you happy.

1:10:36.389 --> 1:10:40.060
Do you think that maybe
being happy is the thing

1:10:40.093 --> 1:10:43.430
that makes your prayers heard?

1:10:50.536 --> 1:10:54.674
So, do
you know why you're here yet?
